# MyFinanceTracker API — run requests from VS / VS Code (REST Client) / Rider.
# Base URL must match launchSettings (http profile uses port 5010).
# After Login, copy AccessToken into @token for protected routes.
# Enums are sent as numbers (default System.Text.Json): AccountType 0=Checking,1=Savings,2=CreditCard,3=Cash | CurrencyCode 0=USD,1=EUR | TransactionType 0=Income,1=Expense

@MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5010
@token = YOUR_JWT_AFTER_LOGIN

### Auth — Register (no JWT)
POST {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "YourPassword1!",
  "confirmPassword": "YourPassword1!",
  "enableNotifications": false
}

###

### Auth — Login (no JWT) — paste accessToken into @token above for requests below
POST {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "YourPassword1!"
}

###

### Accounts — list (optional: ?includeInactive=true)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Accounts
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Accounts — get by id (replace GUID)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Accounts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Accounts — create
POST {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Main checking",
  "accountType": 0,
  "currency": 0,
  "initialBalance": 1000
}

###

### Accounts — update (replace GUID)
PUT {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Accounts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Main checking",
  "accountType": 0,
  "currency": 0,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Accounts — delete (replace GUID)
DELETE {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Accounts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Categories — list (optional: ?includeInactive=true)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Categories
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Categories — get by id (replace GUID)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Categories/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Categories — create (transactionType: 0=Income, 1=Expense)
POST {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "type": 1
}

###

### Categories — update (replace GUID)
PUT {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Categories/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "type": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Categories — delete (replace GUID)
DELETE {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Categories/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Transactions — list (all query params optional: accountId, categoryId, from, to — ISO 8601 dates)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Transactions — list with filters
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions?accountId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&categoryId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002&from=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2025-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Transactions — get by id (replace GUID)
GET {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Transactions — create (replace accountId/categoryId with real GUIDs from Accounts/Categories)
POST {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "accountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "type": 1,
  "amount": 42.50,
  "transactionDate": "2025-02-16T12:00:00Z",
  "description": "Coffee"
}

###

### Transactions — update (replace GUIDs)
PUT {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "accountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "type": 1,
  "amount": 45.00,
  "transactionDate": "2025-02-16T12:00:00Z",
  "description": "Coffee + pastry"
}

###

### Transactions — delete (replace GUID)
DELETE {{MyFinanceTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Transactions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
